      "rationale": "Continuum solid mechanics with bilinear isotropic hardening for Ti-6Al-4V and augmented Lagrange frictional contact is well-established for pedicle screw F1717 simulations. Large-deformation (NLGEOM ON) formulation captures post-yield behavior. Fluid, thermal, and dynamic effects are negligible at 10 mm/min quasi-static loading; exclusion justified."
